title: NFL draft, rumors, sure things

description:
Colin discusses the NFL draft, rumors of the Dolphins trying to move up, and players that should be a sure thing in the NFL. Guests include Jay Glazer, Daniel Jeremiah, Jordan Palmer, and Terry Bradshaw.
